-- Molina, Cearley Explain Concept of `The Skivvies' (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-11-22T20:58:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-22/molina-cearley-explain-concept-of-the-skivvies-audio-.html
Lauren Molina and Nick Cearley, the 
creators of "The Skivvies," explain the concept behind their 
creation of their performance group, in which performers strip 
down to their underwear for their shows. Cearley and Molina talk
with Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  and Vonnie Quinn on Bloomberg 
Radio's "The Hays Advantage."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 06:34
 